Love this song, rings so true for me, Demi if u read this, I have been a fan from the beginning and your current music is AMAZING, I was in a bad relationship with a very abusive man, had a son, so I felt I had to stay for him, my friends warned me, but I clndt or wldnt listen.  Then I found my saving Grace, my husband and we will be married 14 years but, even though he isn't unfaithful, or physically, emotionally and physiologically  abuse me, we have grown so far apart we now have a son together 15 and he adopted my oldest 20 US Army Solider, I Love him, I am in Love with him, but I don't think he is still in Love with me.  I don't blame him, as in 2010 I had to have a complete hysterectomy due to endometriosis and needless to say it has been nightmare for everyone since, then I found out I had Hashimotos an auto-immune disease of my Thyroid, well had to have a Thyrpoidectomy, let me point out I have always been about 100-110lbs, between the hysterectomy and thyroidectomy I have gained close to 70lbs and it is so overwhelmingly mentally and physically I am always angry.  It doesn't stop there before the thyroid issues (which controls your metabolism) I was told I had a microadenoma in my pituitary gland, if u dont already know that is a small tumor on my pituitary gland, which is located in my brain, good thing is it has never changed in size, but the pituitary gland tells your thyroid(which I don't have) to do it's part, like to get your metabolism going, I take synthetic thyroid hormones, but it doesn't really help, so after working 40+hours a week I am so exhausted, but he doesn't understand, he thinks I am just being lazy and FAT, it doesnt stop there, my adrenal glands are also not functioning as they should so I have low cortisol, how do u fix that they prescribe u hydrocortisone, which is a steroid and everyone knows that makes u gain even more weight so I refuse to take it, which in turns causes severe joint pain and after a long day at work I get out of the car looking and feeling like I am 80, his words exactly.  I don't want to go to bed at 3pm when I get home, but I am so tired and in pain that i just dont want to do anything, i rarely leave the house bcse I hate the way I look, nothing fits and I know he does not want to be seen with me.  What happened for better or for worse.  Don't think all I do is complain, but when your body is working against itself and nobody understands and u feel all alone, I just dont know what to do.  I have to get this weight off bcse it is cause a HUGE strain on my body, causing me extreme anxiety and medically I am afraid I am going to have a heart attack.  I hope u see this or someone in your circle does, bcse I would love to know what u did, to get back in shape, I need this for me, physically, mentally, emotionally and medically, as well to get my life back.  Thank you for listening, even if u dont see this.  Jennifer jmlakos@gmail

This video is about Demi saying before she could be ready for a relationship, she needs to love herself. Love isn't something that completes you (or at least it shouldn't be).
